claim.claim-text:
1. A balance filter packaging chip, comprising:
a device substrate;
at least one balance filter mounted on the device substrate;
at least one bonding layer stacked on at least one certain area of the device substrate;
a packaging substrate comprising a cavity formed over the at least one balance filter, and combined with the device substrate by the at least one bonding layer;
at least one balun disposed at a given area above the packaging substrate; and
an insulator layer which covers entirely the at least one balun.
